---
description:  Guidelines for using Shadcn UI components in Next.js projects
globs: **/*.{ts,tsx}
---
- Follow Shadcn UI's component structure and naming conventions
- Customize components using the provided props and slots
- Extend Shadcn UI components with your own styles using Tailwind classes
- Use Shadcn UI's dark mode variants for consistent theming
- Implement accessibility features provided by Shadcn UI components
